fcb_fab_flexible_advantages_bottom_title: All about High Frequency/High Speed PCBs
fcb_fab_flexible_advantages_bottom_word_: • High frequency/high speed PCBs are special circuit boards used to transmit and receive 50MHz to 100GHz high-speed/micwrowave/radio frequency signals.
• Have a small and stable dielectric constant (Dk), which prevents signal transmission delay.
• Have small dielectric loss (Df), which reduces the signal loss.
• Use materials with a low coefficient of thermal expansion (CTE) and have good thermal/chemical resistance.
• Have a high impact and peel strength.
• Typical applications include communications industries (smartphone, signal tower, radar...) and microwave industries (backhaul, sensor, adapter...).
